      <p class="subhead">round-half-to-even($arg as numeric?, $precision as xs:integer) &#8594; numeric?</p>
      <p>Rounds a numeric value to the nearest multiple of ten to the power of minus <code>$precision</code>, rounding x.5 towards
               positive infinity.</p>
